<h1>Disputed sightings</h1>
<p class="subhead">Bylaw VIII.</p>

<blockquote class="society-note">
  Unverified. The Society does not endorse.
</blockquote>

<p>
  Words have no bodies. The Society's archive nonetheless documents the
  human — and apparently not only human — compulsion to give them bodies
  anyway. When a member submits a shaky sketch of a word they claim to
  have seen, it is filed here.
</p>

<p>
  <em>No disputed sightings have been filed yet.</em>
</p>
